data.description: Country living. Quiet cul-de-sac. Bring your horses-property has stalls and barn. Kitchen has great view of pasture to the back.  Designer upgrades: wood floors, tile in wet areas, pull out shelves, lots of storage.  Master has whirlpool tub, separate shower with body sprays.  Walk-in master closet. Energy efficient with foam insulated walls.  Home office. 20x16 shed with 3 bay carport (currently used as horse stalls).  Outside city limits. No city taxes.
